<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Recuperar Contraseña | CARSIL Equipos y Servicios</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Recupera el acceso a tu cuenta del sistema CARSIL.">
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap"
        rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #3B49DF;
            --primary-dark: #2d38b0;
            --accent: #7C3AED;
            --accent2: #06b6d4;
            --navy: #0f172a;
            --panel-bg: #1e2a4a;
            --panel-bg2: #162040;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --gray-100: #f8fafc;
            --gray-200: #e2e8f0;
            --gray-400: #94a3b8;
            --gray-600: #475569;
            --gray-800: #1e293b;
            --success: #10b981;
            --warning: #f59e0b;
        }

        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "SF Pro Display", "Segoe UI", Roboto, "Helvetica Neue", Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: var(--gray-200);
            background-image:
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 0%, rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.12) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 0%, rgba(139, 92, 246, 0.10) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 100% 100%, rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.08) 0px, transparent 50%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 0% 100%, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.08) 0px, transparent 50%);
            background-attachment: fixed;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* ===================== MAIN CARD ===================== */
        .login-card {
            width: min(960px, 98vw);
            min-height: 600px;
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            border-radius: 24px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 32px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.25), 0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            background: var(--white);
        }

        /* ===================== LEFT PANEL ===================== */
        .left-panel {
            padding: 3rem 3rem 2.5rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: space-between;
            background: var(--white);
        }

        .brand {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
        }

        .brand-logo {
            height: 44px;
            width: auto;
            object-fit: contain;
        }

        /* Icon circle */
        .icon-circle {
            width: 64px;
            height: 64px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.1), rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.12));
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.15);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .icon-circle i {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .form-area h1 {
            font-size: 1.75rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--gray-800);
            margin-bottom: 0.4rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.5px;
        }

        .form-area .subtitle {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--gray-400);
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Alert info */
        .alert-info-custom {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.07), rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.07));
            border: 1px solid rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 0.85rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: var(--primary-dark);
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .alert-info-custom i {
            margin-top: 1px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        /* Alert error */
        .alert-error {
            background: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #b91c1c;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.5rem;
        }

        .field-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            margin-bottom: 0.45rem;
            display: block;
        }

        .field-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .input-wrapper {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-wrapper .field-icon {
            position: absolute;
            left: 14px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            color: var(--gray-400);
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .form-input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.75rem 1rem 0.75rem 2.75rem;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--gray-200);
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 0.92rem;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            color: var(--gray-800);
            background: var(--white);
            transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            outline: none;
        }

        .form-input::placeholder {
            color: #cbd5e1;
        }

        .form-input:focus {
            border-color: var(--primary);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.12);
        }

        .btn-submit {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 0.85rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary) 0%, var(--accent) 100%);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            color: var(--white);
            font-size: 0.95rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        }

        .btn-submit::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15) 0%, transparent 60%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .btn-submit:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 28px rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-submit:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .btn-submit i {
            margin-right: 0.5rem;
        }

        .back-link {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
        }

        .back-link:hover {
            color: var(--primary);
        }

        .back-link i {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        /* Steps info */
        .steps-box {
            background: var(--gray-100);
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 1rem 1.1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        .steps-box-title {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }

        .step-item {
            display: flex;
            align-items: flex-start;
            gap: 0.65rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.55rem;
        }

        .step-item:last-child {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }

        .step-num {
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary), var(--accent));
            color: white;
            font-size: 0.65rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            margin-top: 1px;
        }

        .step-text {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--gray-600);
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .footer-left {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: var(--gray-400);
            margin-top: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* ===================== RIGHT PANEL ===================== */
        .right-panel {
            background: linear-gradient(150deg, var(--panel-bg) 0%, var(--panel-bg2) 100%);
            padding: 2.5rem 2.25rem 2rem;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .right-panel::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 320px;
            height: 320px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.35) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: -80px;
            right: -80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .right-panel::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 220px;
            height: 220px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(6, 182, 212, 0.2) 0%, transparent 70%);
            bottom: 60px;
            left: -60px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .right-panel-text h2 {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--white);
            line-height: 1.3;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            letter-spacing: -0.4px;
        }

        .right-panel-text p {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
            line-height: 1.6;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }

        /* AI badge */
        .ai-badge {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.4rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3), rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.3));
            border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.4);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 0.3rem 0.75rem;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #c4b5fd;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            width: fit-content;
        }

        .ai-badge i {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }

        /* ===== SECURITY ILLUSTRATION ===== */
        .dash-container {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            border-radius: 14px;
            padding: 1.25rem;
            flex: 1;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.85rem;
            backdrop-filter: blur(4px);
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        /* Security header */
        .sec-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            padding-bottom: 0.85rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
        }

        .sec-icon-wrap {
            width: 42px;
            height: 42px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.4), rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.4));
            border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .sec-icon-wrap i {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #c4b5fd;
        }

        .sec-header-text .sec-title {
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--white);
        }

        .sec-header-text .sec-sub {
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45);
        }

        /* Process steps */
        .process-steps {
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            gap: 0.6rem;
        }

        .proc-step {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.07);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 0.65rem 0.85rem;
            transition: background 0.2s;
        }

        .proc-step.active {
            background: rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.2);
            border-color: rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.35);
        }

        .proc-step.done {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.1);
            border-color: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
        }

        .proc-step-icon {
            width: 30px;
            height: 30px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }

        .proc-step.idle .proc-step-icon {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.4);
        }

        .proc-step.active .proc-step-icon {
            background: rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.3);
            color: #a5b4fc;
        }

        .proc-step.done .proc-step-icon {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.25);
            color: #6ee7b7;
        }

        .proc-step-info {
            flex: 1;
        }

        .proc-step-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
            margin-bottom: 1px;
        }

        .proc-step-desc {
            font-size: 0.62rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.38);
        }

        .proc-step-badge {
            font-size: 0.58rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            padding: 2px 7px;
            border-radius: 20px;
        }

        .badge-active {
            background: rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.3);
            color: #a5b4fc;
        }

        .badge-done {
            background: rgba(16, 185, 129, 0.2);
            color: #6ee7b7;
        }

        .badge-pend {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.35);
        }

        /* Security tip */
        .sec-tip {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.12), rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.06));
            border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 0.7rem 0.85rem;
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            align-items: flex-start;
        }

        .sec-tip i {
            color: #fcd34d;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-top: 1px;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .sec-tip-text {
            font-size: 0.68rem;
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }

        .sec-tip-text strong {
            color: #fcd34d;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        /* Floating dots */
        @keyframes floatDot {

            0%,
            100% {
                transform: translateY(0);
            }

            50% {
                transform: translateY(-8px);
            }
        }

        .float-dot {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            opacity: 0.18;
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .fd1 {
            width: 10px;
            height: 10px;
            background: #a78bfa;
            top: 20%;
            left: 15%;
            animation: floatDot 3.5s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        .fd2 {
            width: 6px;
            height: 6px;
            background: #67e8f9;
            top: 60%;
            right: 12%;
            animation: floatDot 4s ease-in-out infinite 0.8s;
        }

        .fd3 {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            background: #3B49DF;
            bottom: 20%;
            left: 30%;
            animation: floatDot 5s ease-in-out infinite 1.5s;
        }

        /* ===================== ANIMATIONS ===================== */
        @keyframes fadeUp {
            from {
                opacity: 0;
                transform: translateY(18px);
            }

            to {
                opacity: 1;
                transform: translateY(0);
            }
        }

        .left-panel {
            animation: fadeUp 0.55s ease both;
        }

        .right-panel {
            animation: fadeUp 0.65s ease both 0.1s;
        }

        .dash-container {
            animation: fadeUp 0.7s ease both 0.25s;
        }

        /* Pulse on active step */
        @keyframes pulse {

            0%,
            100% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 0 rgba(59, 73, 223, 0.4);
            }

            50% {
                box-shadow: 0 0 0 5px rgba(59, 73, 223, 0);
            }
        }

        .proc-step.active .proc-step-icon {
            animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
        }

        /* ===================== RESPONSIVE ===================== */
        @media (max-width: 730px) {
            body {
                overflow-y: auto;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }

            .login-card {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
                border-radius: 0;
                min-height: 100vh;
                width: 100%;
            }

            .right-panel {
                display: none;
            }

            .left-panel {
                padding: 2.5rem 1.75rem;
                min-height: 100vh;
            }
        }

        @media (max-width: 900px) and (min-width: 731px) {
            .login-card {
                grid-template-columns: 1.1fr 0.9fr;
            }

            .left-panel {
                padding: 2.5rem 2rem;
            }

            .right-panel {
                padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
            }

            .right-panel-text h2 {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>

    <div class="login-card">

        <!-- ==================== LEFT PANEL ==================== -->
        <div class="left-panel">
            <div>
                <!-- Brand -->
                <div class="brand">
                    <img src="/img/Carsil.png" alt="Logo CARSIL" class="brand-logo">
                </div>

                <!-- Form area -->
                <div class="form-area">
                    <!-- Icon -->
                    <div class="icon-circle">
                        <i class="fas fa-unlock-alt"></i>
                    </div>

                    <h1>Recuperar contraseña</h1>
                    <p class="subtitle">
                        Ingresa tu correo registrado y te enviaremos un enlace para restablecer tu acceso de forma
                        segura.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Alert mensaje (info o error) -->
                    <% if (typeof mensaje !=='undefined' && mensaje) { %>
                        <div class="alert-info-custom" role="alert">
                            <i class="fas fa-circle-check"></i>
                            <%= mensaje %>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>

                            <!-- Steps box -->
                            <div class="steps-box">
                                <div class="steps-box-title">¿Cómo funciona?</div>
                                <div class="step-item">
                                    <div class="step-num">1</div>
                                    <div class="step-text">Ingresa tu correo electrónico registrado.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step-item">
                                    <div class="step-num">2</div>
                                    <div class="step-text">Recibirás un enlace de verificación en tu bandeja.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step-item">
                                    <div class="step-num">3</div>
                                    <div class="step-text">Sigue el enlace para crear tu nueva contraseña.</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <form method="POST" action="/recuperar" autocomplete="off">
                                <div class="field-group">
                                    <label class="field-label" for="correo">Correo electrónico</label>
                                    <div class="input-wrapper">
                                        <i class="fas fa-envelope field-icon"></i>
                                        <input type="email" class="form-input" id="correo" name="correo" required
                                            autofocus placeholder="usuario@carsil.com"
                                            value="<%= typeof correo !== 'undefined' && correo ? correo : '' %>">
                                    </div>
                                </div>

                                <button type="submit" class="btn-submit" id="btn-submit">
                                    <i class="fas fa-paper-plane"></i> Enviar enlace de recuperación
                                </button>
                            </form>

                            <a href="/login" class="back-link">
                                <i class="fas fa-arrow-left"></i> Volver al inicio de sesión
                            </a>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Footer -->
            <div class="footer-left">
                &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> CARSIL Equipos y Servicios. Todos los derechos reservados.
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- ==================== RIGHT PANEL ==================== -->
        <div class="right-panel">
            <div class="float-dot fd1"></div>
            <div class="float-dot fd2"></div>
            <div class="float-dot fd3"></div>

            <div class="right-panel-text">
                <div class="ai-badge">
                    <i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i> Recuperación segura
                </div>
                <h2>Tu seguridad es nuestra prioridad.</h2>
                <p>El proceso de recuperación está protegido con verificación de identidad y enlace de un solo uso para
                    garantizar tu acceso seguro.</p>
            </div>

            <!-- Security process visualization -->
            <div class="dash-container">

                <!-- Header -->
                <div class="sec-header">
                    <div class="sec-icon-wrap">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-halved"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="sec-header-text">
                        <div class="sec-title">Proceso de recuperación</div>
                        <div class="sec-sub">Verificación en 3 pasos</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Process steps -->
                <div class="process-steps">
                    <div class="proc-step active">
                        <div class="proc-step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-envelope"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="proc-step-info">
                            <div class="proc-step-label">Validar correo</div>
                            <div class="proc-step-desc">Verificamos que el correo esté registrado</div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="proc-step-badge badge-active">En curso</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="proc-step idle">
                        <div class="proc-step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-link"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="proc-step-info">
                            <div class="proc-step-label">Enviar enlace único</div>
                            <div class="proc-step-desc">Link con expiración de 30 minutos</div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="proc-step-badge badge-pend">Pendiente</span>
                    </div>

                    <div class="proc-step idle">
                        <div class="proc-step-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-lock"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="proc-step-info">
                            <div class="proc-step-label">Nueva contraseña</div>
                            <div class="proc-step-desc">Crea una contraseña segura y única</div>
                        </div>
                        <span class="proc-step-badge badge-pend">Pendiente</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Security tip -->
                <div class="sec-tip">
                    <i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation"></i>
                    <div class="sec-tip-text">
                        <strong>Consejo de seguridad:</strong> Nunca compartas el enlace de recuperación. Si no
                        solicitaste este proceso, ignora el correo. El enlace expira en <strong>30 minutos</strong>.
                    </div>
                </div>

            </div><!-- /dash-container -->
        </div><!-- /right-panel -->

    </div><!-- /login-card -->

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script>
        // Loading state on submit
        document.querySelector('form').addEventListener('submit', function () {
            const btn = document.getElementById('btn-submit');
            btn.innerHTML = '<i class="fas fa-spinner fa-spin"></i> Enviando...';
            btn.disabled = true;
        });
    </script>
</body>

